data.persona: I am a tiny spider.  I live in the dark dungeon of the castle.  It is cold and dark, but I like it.  No one ever bothers me here.
data.description:
You are in the Jungle.
Full of natural beauty and danger, the jungle holds many rewards and risks. From beautiful awe inspiring fauna to the worlds most deadly creatures.
The creature and the monkey are here.

You are carrying nothing.

data.short_motivation: I want to go to the depths of the jungle with the monkey.
data.mid_motivation: I want to see if the branches that the monkey lives in contain a lot of insects that I can eat.
data.long_motivation: I want to find a better place to set up spiderwebs, since every spiderweb takes a lot of effort to make and I want to be able to feed myself.
